data.title: HW001 : Paramount Pictures Stars
data.meta_description: Actors of Paramount Pictures Studio for the studio’s 75th anniversary in Hollywood, 1987. Featuring Elizabeth Taylor, Harrison Ford, Faye Dunaway, Robert De Niro, Gregory Peck, Robin Williams and many others.
